---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../../css/services.css";
---

<Layout
  title="Web & Network Design | GeneralSoft UAE"
  description="Professional web development and network design services in the UAE. Custom websites, e-commerce solutions, and secure network infrastructure."
  path="/services/web-design/"
  image="/img/og-web-design.jpg"
>
  <section class="service-content" id="software-services">
    <div class="service-section" style="margin-top: 120px;">
      <h2 class="service-title">Web & Network Design</h2>
      <p>
        Your website and network infrastructure are the digital foundation of
        your business. At GeneralSoft, we build websites that are fast,
        secure, and conversion-optimized, and we design network architectures
        that are reliable, scalable, and secure. From simple informational
        sites to complex web applications and enterprise network design, we
        deliver solutions that perform.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our web development practice spans three decades — from early
        e-commerce platforms to modern static-site architectures and
        progressive web applications. We combine this experience with current
        best practices in performance optimization, accessibility, and search
        engine optimization.
      </p>

      <h3>Our Capabilities</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Custom Website Development</h4>
          <p>
            Fast, responsive websites built with modern frameworks including
            Astro, Angular, and Bootstrap.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>E-Commerce Solutions</h4>
          <p>
            Online stores with secure payment processing, inventory management,
            and supplier feed integration.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Web Applications</h4>
          <p>
            Full-stack web applications with RESTful APIs, real-time features,
            and cloud deployment.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Network Design</h4>
          <p>
            Secure network architecture including DNS, VPN, firewall
            configuration, and WAN/LAN design.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Projects Proof Section -->
      <div class="projects-proof">
        <h3>Proven Web Delivery — Projects Completed</h3>
        <p>
          Our web portfolio spans e-commerce platforms, university portals,
          and corporate websites built for performance and scale.
        </p>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Website Development — GeneralSoft RAKEZ</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Jan 2025 – Jan 2025</span>
            <span class="role">Web Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Designed and developed the GeneralSoft corporate website using
            modern web technologies. Built with a focus on performance,
            bilingual support (English/Arabic), and lead generation. The site
            showcases our full range of services with a clean, professional
            design optimized for the UAE market.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">HTML</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">CSS</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">JS</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Astro</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Responsive Design</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>E-Commerce Solutions — Retail Website Components</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Oct 2000 – Jan 2001</span>
            <span class="role">Designer & Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Built website components for a retail e-commerce platform. Developed
            systems to convert supplier feeds into XML, update retail catalogs
            from supplier data, and validate catalogs prior to web publishing.
            The solution automated the entire product lifecycle from supplier
            ingestion to customer-facing display.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">JSP</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Java</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">PL/SQL</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">XML</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Perl</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>University Portal — California State University</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Feb 2001 – Apr 2001</span>
            <span class="role">Architect & Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Developed web portal components for California State University
            (CSU) enabling student registration, enrollment, course management,
            instructor administration, online teaching material publishing, and
            customer care. Built with JSP, Java, and PL/SQL.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">JSP</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Java</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">PL/SQL</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Web Portal</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Web 2.0 & PDA — Realty Industry Application</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Sep 2007 – Dec 2007</span>
            <span class="role">Architect & Lead Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Built a shrink-wrap web application for the European realty industry
            enabling landlords to upload real-estate inventory data from PDAs
            and provide customer service via a Web 2.0 site. BizTalk served as
            the process manager for license management and contract
            documentation. Used GIS for assigning property inspections to
            inspectors.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">ASP.NET</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">AJAX</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Silverlight</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">BizTalk</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">GIS</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Compact Framework</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Technology Stack</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> Astro, Angular, Bootstrap, JavaScript/TypeScript</li>
        <li><strong>Backend:</strong> .NET, Java, NodeJS, Python</li>
        <li><strong>Hosting:</strong> Azure, AWS, GCP, dedicated servers</li>
        <li><strong>Networking:</strong> DNS, DNSSEC, HTTP/2, HTTP/3, TLS 1.3, IPv4/IPv6</li>
        <li><strong>Security:</strong> OAuth 2.0, SSL/TLS, WAF, DDoS protection</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="faq-container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Common questions about our web and network design services.
        </p>

        <div class="faq-list">
          <details>
            <summary>Do you build bilingual websites (English/Arabic)?</summary>
            <p>
              Yes. We have extensive experience building bilingual websites with
              full RTL support for Arabic. Our current corporate website is a
              prime example — fully bilingual with proper Arabic typography,
              right-to-left layout, and localized content.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details>
            <summary>Can you optimize my website for search engines?</summary>
            <p>
              Absolutely. We build websites with SEO best practices baked in
              from the start — semantic HTML, proper heading structure, meta
              tags, structured data (Schema.org), optimized images, fast load
              times, and mobile-first responsive design.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details>
            <summary>Do you provide hosting and maintenance?</summary>
            <p>
              Yes. We offer managed hosting on Azure or AWS with automated
              backups, security updates, performance monitoring, and content
              updates. We also provide domain registration and DNS management.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-content">
        <h2>Let's Build Something Great Together</h2>
        <p>
          Ready to establish your digital presence? Get in touch with our
          team today.
        </p>
        <div class="contact-info">
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="contact-item-icon">🌐</div><strong>Website</strong><a
              href="https://generalsoft.ae">generalsoft.ae</a
            >
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <a href="/contact/"
              ><div class="contact-item-icon">📧</div><strong>Contact Us</strong
              ><br />Get in touch</a
            >
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="contact-item-icon">📍</div><strong>Location</strong
            ><span>Ras Al Khaimah</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
